      <title>中国有望扩大预算并降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/china-seen-expanding-budget-and-cutting-rates-after-stimulus-vow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国高层领导人发出多年来最大胆的刺激信号之后，中国明年的预算赤字可能会升至30年来的最高水平，并进行自2015年以来最大幅度的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/china-seen-expanding-budget-and-cutting-rates-after-stimulus-vow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 04:43:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>退税取消前中国铝出口激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/china-s-aluminum-exports-surge-as-traders-try-to-beat-tax-tweak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本月初取消的税收折扣，出口商纷纷涌向中国市场以获益，11月份中国铝出口量接近创纪录水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/china-s-aluminum-exports-surge-as-traders-try-to-beat-tax-tweak</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 04:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡斯皮银行主导的网上零售贷款业务受到哈萨克斯坦监管机构的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/kaspi-led-online-retail-lending-draws-kazakh-watchdog-s-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦蓬勃发展的在线市场之所以蓬勃发展，部分原因在于一种受欢迎的融资方式，由于担心通胀和不断增加的消费者债务负担，这种融资方式目前受到监管机构的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/kaspi-led-online-retail-lending-draws-kazakh-watchdog-s-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度任命新印度储备银行行长后，债券市场可能因降息押注而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/bonds-may-gain-on-rate-cut-bets-after-india-names-new-rbi-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政府任命职业官僚桑杰马洛特拉 (Sanjay Malhotra) 为印度储备银行新任行长后，分析师押注印度将降息，印度债券有望上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/bonds-may-gain-on-rate-cut-bets-after-india-names-new-rbi-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
